18/06/2004
SARAJEVO, Bosnia and Herzegovina (BiH) -- High Representative Paddy Ashdown has appointed Kalman Kocsis to supervise the intelligence reform in BiH. 
In a statement Thursday (17 June), the Office of the High Representative said Kocsis will report directly and regularly to Ashdown about progress made in implementing recently passed legislation concerning intelligence and security. 
(OHR Sources, Fena - 17/06/04)
